Interface EjbRefType

public interface EjbRefType

A representation of the model object 'Ejb Ref Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Ejb Ref Name
  • Ejb Ref Type
  • Home
  • Remote
  • Ejb Link
  • Id
